Knowledge corpus — copyright & fair use posture
------------------------------------------------------------------------

Knowledge cards in data/corpus.json are LLM-paraphrased standalone
distillations exported from the Knowledge Atlas pipeline. They are:

  - Transformative (rewritten into clean modern English)
  - Non-substitutive (always attributed to source YouTube videos)
  - Educational (defensive literacy and research)
  - Not raw transcripts (transcripts are never distributed)

Original video content remains the property of respective YouTube creators.
Short anchor quotes (≤30 words) function as citation anchors, not substitutes
for the original works.

Users must comply with YouTube Terms of Service when accessing source videos.

